      <url>/2021/07/26/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%80%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E5%A4%96%E7%A0%94%E7%89%88%E5%BF%85%E4%BF%AE%E4%B8%80%E7%9F%AD%E8%AF%AD%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="to-do结构"><a href="#to-do结构" class="headerlink" title="to do结构"></a>to do结构</h1><h2 id="UNIT-1"><a href="#UNIT-1" class="headerlink" title="UNIT 1"></a>UNIT 1</h2><ol><li><p><strong>in one’s eagerness to do sth.</strong><br> <strong>be eager to do sth.</strong><br> <em>渴望做某事</em><br> eg. I woke up early and rushed out of the door   in my eagerness to get to know my new         school.<br> eg. He was eager to make up the missed lessons after a week’s absence from school.</p></li><li><p><strong>it’s one’s turn to do sth.</strong><br> <em>轮到某人做某事</em><br> eg. It’s his turn to take care of the baby in night.</p></li><li><p><strong>be curious to do sth.</strong><br> <em>很想做某事</em><br> eg. People gathered  around,curious to know what was happening.</p></li><li><p><strong>depend on sb. to do sth.</strong><br> <em>依靠/指望某人做某事</em><br> eg. If our parents do everything for us children,we won’t learn to depend on ourselves to do        anything.</p></li><li><p><strong>have confidence to do sth.</strong><br> <em>有信心做某事</em><br> eg. We have confidence to finish the task.</p></li><li><p><strong>volunteer to do sth.</strong><br> <em>自愿/主动提出做某事</em><br> eg. According to the research,people feel good when they volunteer to do something             meaningful for other people.</p></li><li><p><strong>apply to do sth.</strong><br> <em>申请做某事</em><br> eg. I’ve applied to become a volunteer at the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympic Games.</p></li><li><p><strong>be scheduled to do sth.</strong><br> <em>预计做某事</em><br> eg. The professor is scheduled to arrive in Shanghai at 10 o’clock.</p></li><li><p><strong>be about to do sth.</strong><br> <em>即将做某事</em><br> eg. Lisa graduated from our school last June and is about to go to college in Nee York.</p></li><li><p><strong>be frightened to do sth.</strong><br><em>害怕做某事</em><br>eg. Don’t be frightened to go ahead,for there is always something special waiting for us.</p></li><li><p><strong>select sb. to do sth.</strong><br><em>挑选某人做某事</em><br>eg. We selected him to take part in the English contest.</p></li><li><p><strong>struggle to do sth.</strong><br><em>努力做某事</em><br>eg. My father struggled to support a large family on very low income(收入) several years ago.</p></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
